tags.notes: the seats are divided, as many of these benches are in downtown Vancouver. The benches are earthed into the ground. The ground is concrete.

this is a concrete block where people can sit on. It has metal clippings that appears to be a dividing line for people sitting on the block, however it is probably an attempt to discourage skateboarders from using the block as a ramp for their tricks.

This bench does not have dividing armrests, a rare sight in downtown Vancouver.
